  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course it was all a dream. No coherent story. No motivation. Nothing made sense. No one around.<br>Just ran, or tried to. Heavy legs. Barely able to move. But to jump felt like flying.<br>So collect hearts. Collect brains. Use power-ups. Success is simple, so long as success is enough <br><br>---<br><br>configurable platform game:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >side-scroll, third-person, first-person</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >individual levels, zone, or full campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >high pressure time limits and health, or turn them off for casual terrain traversal</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >overwhelming OSD can be reduced or disabled</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >mouse sensitivity and fov adjustment, and head bob/screen shake toggles</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course it was all a dream. No coherent story. No motivation. Nothing made sense. No one around.<br>Just ran, or tried to. Heavy legs. Barely able to move. But to jump felt like flying.<br>So collect hearts. Collect brains. Use power-ups. Success is simple, so long as success is enough <br><br>---<br><br>configurable platform game:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >side-scroll, third-person, first-person</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >individual levels, zone, or full campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >high pressure time limits and health, or turn them off for casual terrain traversal</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >overwhelming OSD can be reduced or disabled</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >mouse sensitivity and fov adjustment, and head bob/screen shake toggles</p></li></ul>",
